<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-a-manner">in a ... manner</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>用…的方式 / 态度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They worked in an orderly manner. 
他们有条不紊地工作。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She greeted me in a friendly manner. 
她友好地和我打招呼。</p></div></div>